snippet.title: Arcade Archives TERRA FORCE
snippet.description:
"TERRA FORCE" is a shooting game that was released from Nichibutsu in 1987.
A new element, to attack by going back and forth between vertical and horizontal scroll stages, was a topic at that time.
Wipe out enemies with hyper missiles with destructive super power.

Arcade Archives Official Website
http://www.hamster.co.jp/american_hamster/arcadearchives/
